 HTML :
<div> → Wraps product details for styling.
<img> → Displays the product image.
<h2> → Shows the product name.
<p> → Provides product description.
<span> → Highlights price.
<button> → Adds to cart or buy option.

CSS :
flexbox/grid → Aligns product layout.
box-shadow → Gives a card-like effect.
hover effects → Changes button color on hover.
